    "en": {
      "name": "Witchcrafter Marka",
      "effect": "You can Tribute this card from your hand or field; add 1 \"Witchcrafter\" Field or Continuous Spell from your Deck to your hand. If a face-up \"Witchcrafter\" monster(s) you control leaves the field by an opponent's card effect, while this card is in your GY (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card (but banish it when it leaves the field), and if you do, Tribute 1 monster your opponent controls. You can only use each effect of \"Witchcrafter Marka\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
